        "content": "<p>Do you think my formalization of the <a href=\"https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/plural-quant/#ex3\">Geach-Kaplan sentence</a> is correct?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Mathlib.Data.Set.Basic</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">opaque</span> <span class=\"n\">Human</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span>\n<span class=\"n\">opaque</span> <span class=\"n\">isCritic</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Human</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"kt\">Prop</span>\n<span class=\"n\">opaque</span> <span class=\"n\">Admires</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Human</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">Human</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"kt\">Prop</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">infix</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">55</span> <span class=\"s2\">\" admires \"</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">Admires</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- the Geach-Kaplan sentence: \"some critics admire only one another\"</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">GKS</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Prop</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"bp\">∃</span> <span class=\"n\">isSomeCritic</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Human</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"kt\">Prop</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∃</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Human</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">isSomeCritic</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">∧</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Human</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">isSomeCritic</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">isCritic</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">∧</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∃</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Human</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"n\">admires</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">∧</span> <span class=\"bp\">∀</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Human</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"n\">admires</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">isSomeCritic</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span> <span class=\"bp\">∧</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">≠</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- restate the proposition `GKS` by using `Set`</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">GKS'</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Prop</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"bp\">∃</span> <span class=\"n\">someCritics</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Set</span> <span class=\"n\">Human</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∃</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Human</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">∈</span> <span class=\"n\">someCritics</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">∧</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Human</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">∈</span> <span class=\"n\">someCritics</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">isCritic</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">∧</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">∃</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Human</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"n\">admires</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">∧</span> <span class=\"bp\">∀</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Human</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"n\">admires</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span> <span class=\"bp\">∈</span> <span class=\"n\">someCritics</span> <span class=\"bp\">∧</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">≠</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- the above two definitions are equivalent</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">GKS</span> <span class=\"bp\">↔</span> <span class=\"n\">GKS'</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">Iff.refl</span> <span class=\"n\">GKS</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
